data.description: “Entertainers Delight”  This single story home is a rare find with gated double RV parking located on both sides The north side of the house even comes with a  clean out connection to the sewer for your RV!!, situated on a dead end street.  The first thing you will notice is the beautiful curb appeal of the front yard! You will love the cheerful open floor plan with laminate flooring & plantation shutters & recessed lighting. Curl up on your favorite chair in your spacious family room as you enjoy the cozy wood burning fireplace with a special gift of a 65” flat screen TV left by the sellers for you to enjoy placed right above your roaring fire.  If you prefer peace & quiet step into your large separate living room.    2 of the 4 bedrooms have an on-suite which would be an added plus for in-law quarters.  2 of the 3 bathrooms have been updated with beautifully tiled walk in showers. For your comfort this home comes with central ac/heat, ceiling fans & an added bonus of paid for solar!!!!!  Your 2 car garage has access to your home or your low maintenance backyard with a spacious 8 X 14 shed to store your extra items.  "LOCATION-LOCATION-"This beautiful “move in ready” home is centrally located within walking distance to shopping, easy freeway access, & just minutes from the metro link stations. You will be close to Montclair Plaza, Golds Gym, Target, Movie theater many good restaurants & much much more!  A perfect house just waiting for you to make it your special home!!!        ( approximate  Sq, Ft. is 2,069)    ( original Sq, Ft. 1,469 per title, & 600 Sq,Ft . per permitted addition)
